{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23141.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day01.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime04","chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-1"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Sorry about last time...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]We did the best we could."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-3"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Let's just get down to business.@In this loop..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-4"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll make sure Miss Miki gives up@on the contract."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-5"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You're going to stop her...?"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-6"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's right."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-7"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It sucks not to have her around as@a Magical Girl to help us in the fight..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-8"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But last time, even with the four of us,@it didn't work out in the end."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-9"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]We need a different approach@to beat Walpurgisnacht."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...I have two questions."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-11"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]If Sayaka Miki doesn't make a contract,@Kyosuke Kamijo's injuries won't be healed."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"motion":101,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-12"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Your meddling is going to change@the course of a person's life."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Are you prepared to accept that?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-14"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I do think his accident was tragic."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-14b"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-15"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]If seeking a miracle only brings about@a bigger tragedy..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I think he needs to accept his own fate."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":230103,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...All right.@As long as you're absolutely sure."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-18"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Now, for the second question..."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":400,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-19"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll convince her."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-20"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Mabayu?"},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I'll convince her, as a friend."},{"chara":[{"id":200902,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Mabayu","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I think now, I'll be able to earn@her trust for sure."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":230103,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvColor":"textHomura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...I see."},{"chara":[{"id":230103,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104207/vo_full_908101-050-24"}],"nameAvLeft":"Homura","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Then, I hope everything turns out well."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
